Documentation

* Tutorial

 The {{{./tutorial.html}Tutorial}} provides a quick start to Jolokia. It
 demonstrates how to deploy a WAR-agent, how to check the installation
 via a Web browser and demonstrates the client usage with a small
 sample Java application.

* Reference Manual
  
 The {{{./reference/html/index.html}reference manual}} contains a comprehensive
 documentation to Jolokia, its agents and client bindings. There is also
 a {{{./reference/pdf/jolokia-reference.pdf}PDF version}}.

* Talks and Screencast

 In this {{{./talks.html}section}} various talks along with slides and some example screencasts
 are collected. They give short impressions what can be done with Jolokia and
 its clients.